Collection of shell scripts to automate few manual and common tasks.

build-jail-base.sh 
 Builds FreeBSD base in /jails/base 
 do make buildworld before !

build-package.sh 
 builds package from port, 
 ensuring enviromental variables 
 and making config before building (to allowed uninterrupted coffeine intake while pkgs are building)

fixit-sshd.sh 
 runs sshd in fixit enviroment to avoid using more confortable work enviroments etc ... 

zfs-gpt-install.sh 
 install freebsd with GPT partition and zfs only disks.
 installs only base system, do after-install config with sysinstall :)



